    <div class="info-card slide-in">
        <p>
            Hi, I'm Amanda!
        </p>
        <br>
        <p>
            Initially intended to be a single show, All Femme Fronted was created in July of 2022 when a bandmate and I trying to come up with unique ideas for shows. As the group was fronted by a woman, we landed on All Femme Fronted: a show featuring acts exclusively with female or gender-diverse leads.
            When the show saw some success in February of 2023, and after following the suggestions of a professor of mine, I decided to start creating show opportunities for musicians. 
            
            <br><br>All Femme Fronted evolved to become a concert series and later, a place to promote local female and gender-diverse musicians and build awareness about cool opportunities for musicians.
            I hope that by showcasing the incredible contributions of our community to Vancouver’s underground music scene I can advocate for more gender-diversity on more local bills, especially in genre scenes where femme representation may be lacking.
            <br><br>I look forward to watching this community evolve, grow, and become stronger together!
        </p>
    </div>
    

    <div class="recent-posts-container slide-in">
        <div class="posts-header">
            <h2>Recent Posts</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="list-container">
            <ul class="post-grid">
                {
                    posts.slice(0, 4).map((post: any, index: number) => (
                        <li
                            class="post slide-in"
                            style={`animation-delay: ${index * 0.1}s`}
                        >
                            <a href={`${post.url}`}>
                                <img
                                    src={post.frontmatter.heroImage}
                                    alt={post.frontmatter.title}
                                    loading="lazy"
                                />
                                <div class="text-content">
                                    <h4 class="title">
                                        {post.frontmatter.title}
                                    </h4>
                                    <p class="subtitle">
                                        {post.frontmatter.subtitle}
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="arrow">
                                    <div class="arrow-top" />
                                    <div class="arrow-bottom" />
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    ))
                }
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>

    @keyframes fadeUpIn {
        0% {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(40px) scale(0.95);
        }
        100% {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
        }
    }

    .slide-in {
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeUpIn 1s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1) forwards;
        will-change: transform, opacity;
    }

    .banner-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .banner-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        margin: 0 4vw;
        max-height: 40vh;
        object-fit: cover;
        object-position: top left;
    }

    .header-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-start; 
        align-items: flex-start;
        background-image: url('../indexbackground.webp');
        background-size: cover;
        min-height: 50vh;
        margin: 2vh 4vw;
        padding: 4vh 2vw; 
        font-size: 1.5em;
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    .info-card {
        margin: 4vh 4vw;
        padding: 2em 2.5em;
        background: linear-gradient(145deg, #242220, #1a1918); /* inner dark background */
        position: relative;
        color: #efeeee;
        font-size: 1.3em;
        line-height: 1.6;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        z-index: 1;

        /* border: 2px solid transparent;
        background-image: 
            linear-gradient(145deg, #242220, #1a1918), 
            linear-gradient(90deg, #a855f7, #ec4899, #f97316); 
        background-origin: border-box;
        background-clip: padding-box, border-box; */
    }

    .info-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }


    .info-card h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-family: "Special Gothic Expanded One", sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.6em;
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .info-card p {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'PPNeueMontreal-Book', sans-serif;
        color: #d1d0cf;
    }



    .text-header {
        max-width: 1200px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .recent-posts-container {
        font-size: 0.8em;
        margin-top: 3vh;
    }

    .posts-header {
        display: flex;
        width: 100%;
        margin-bottom: -20px;
        padding: 0 4vw;
    }

    h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Special Gothic Expanded One", sans-serif;
    }

    * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .list-container {
        display: flex;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .post-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        grid-auto-rows: auto;
        gap: 2em;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0 4vw;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .post {
        list-style: none;
        overflow: hidden;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }

    .post a {
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .post img {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        max-height: 727px;
        aspect-ratio: 4/5;
        object-fit: cover;
        transition: 0.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    .post:hover img {
        opacity: 0.4;
    }

    .arrow {
        width: 10px;
        height: 10px;
        margin-top: 12px;
        position: relative;
        margin-left: auto;
        z-index: 2;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .arrow-top,
    .arrow-bottom {
        background-color: #666;
        height: 4px;
        left: -5px;
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        width: 75%;
    }

    /* global change */
    .arrow-top:after,
    .arrow-bottom:after {
        background-color: #fff;
        content: "";
        height: 100%;
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        transition: all 0.15s;
    }

    .arrow-top {
        transform: rotate(45deg);
        transform-origin: bottom right;
    }

    .arrow-top:after {
        left: 100%;
        right: 0;
        transition-delay: 0s;
    }

    .arrow-bottom {
        transform: rotate(-45deg);
        transform-origin: top right;
    }

    .arrow-bottom:after {
        left: 0;
        right: 100%;
        transition-delay: 0.15s;
    }

    .post:hover .arrow-top:after {
        left: 0;
        transition-delay: 0.15s;
    }

    .post:hover .arrow-bottom:after {
        right: 0;
        transition-delay: 0s;
    }

    .arrow:active {
        transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%) scale(0.9);
    }

    .text-content h4 {
        margin: 0;
        padding-top: 10px;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        display: -webkit-box;
        -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        -webkit-line-clamp: 1;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-overflow: ellipsis;
        font-size: 1.3em;
    }

    .text-content p {
        margin: 0;
        display: -webkit-box;
        -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-overflow: ellipsis;
        font-size: 1em;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1920px) {
        .post-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            padding: 0 4vw;
            gap: 1.5em;
        }

        .posts-header {
            padding: 0 4vw;
        }

        .text-content h4 {
            font-size: 1.4em;
        }

        .text-content p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1022px) {
        .post-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            padding: 0 3vw;
            gap: 1.2em;
        }

        .posts-header {
            padding: 0 3vw;
        }

        .text-content h4 {
            font-size: 1.3em;
        }

        .text-content p {
            font-size: 1.0em;
        }

        .header-container {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 0 3vw;
        }

        .banner-image {
            margin: 0 3vw;
        }
        
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .post-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            padding: 0 3vw;
            gap: 1.4em;
        }

        .posts-header {
            padding: 0 3vw;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        .text-content h4 {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .text-content p {
            font-size: 1.0em;
        }

        .header-container {
            font-size: 1em;
            padding: 3vh 2vw;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 400px) {
        .post-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
            padding: 0 4vw;
            gap: 0.7em;
        }

        .posts-header {
            padding: 5px 4vw;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        .text-content h4 {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .text-content p {
            font-size: 1.0em;
        }

        .header-container {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            padding: 3vh 2vw; 
            margin: 0 4vw;
        }
    }
</style>
